Revision history for Object-Proto-Sugar

0.05	2026-04-12
	- Add accessor_alias keyword for package-level function accessor prefixing
	- accessor_alias applies to accessor, reader, and writer when set to 1
	- Per-class alias preserved across inheritance for import_accessors

0.03	2026-04-05
	- Explictly require type constants to be imported into a package
	- Extend with more sugar constants (porting my MooX::LazierAttributes syntax)

0.02	2026-04-04
	- Add support for defining "has" attributes as arrayref

0.01    Date/time
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

